## Flashing Tasmota
**WARNING:** The devices cannot be flashed with Tuya-Convert at present (2021-12-10).
You will need to flash the `tasmota-ir.bin` firmware to this device via serial (see pinout below).
Use [`tasmota-ir.bin`](http://ota.tasmota.com/tasmota/release/tasmota-ir.bin) firmware for full infrared (IR) functionality.

## Opening case
The case can be opened via 4 clips which are quite tight. See image below.
![NVS-SMARTIR-W2](/assets/images/nivian_NVS-SMARTIR-W2_clips.jpg)
 
## Pinout for flashing via serial
You can temporarily solder jumper cables to the pins denoted in the image below.
![NVS-SMARTIR-W2](/assets/images/nivian_NVS-SMARTIR-W2_pinout.jpg)
